# Natani Simak's formatting style
# Docs: https://clang.llvm.org/docs/ClangFormatStyleOptions.html
---
BasedOnStyle: Google
---
Language: Cpp
AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align
AlignArrayOfStructures: Right

